room_title: Escape room "Brewery Heist" by Green Light Escape Room in Wilmington
room_address: 130 N. Front St. Suite 202 Wilmington, NC 28401
room_description: A modern-day prohibition has halted the production and sale of beer. It’s been a few months now and everyone is out. Rumor has it Wilmington’s oldest brewery has the last reserve. Can you break in and save the beer? We’re all counting on you!
